column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday July 2 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for Mason Headley Rd at Versailles Rd:
column4: Serious injury collision.  Traffic on Mason Headley Rd approaching Versailles Rd is being diverted to the Cardinal Hill parking lot.

column3: Traffic Alert for Mason Headley Rd at Versailles Rd:
column4: The inbound right lane and right turn lane of Versailles Rd are blocked.
